#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:4
msgid "Crashes"
msgstr "崩溃"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:6
msgid "The most common causes of Blender crashes:"
msgstr "引起Blender崩溃的最常见原因:"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:8
msgid "Running out of memory."
msgstr "运行内存不足。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:9
msgid "Issues with graphics hardware or drivers."
msgstr "图形硬件或驱动程序的问题。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:10
msgid "Bugs in Blender."
msgstr "Blender里的bug。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:13
msgid "Firstly, you may be able to recover your work with :menuselection:`File --> Recover Last Session`."
msgstr "首先，你可以通过 :menuselection:`文件 --> 恢复最后一次会话` 来恢复你的工作。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:15
msgid ""
"To prevent the problem from happening again, you can check that the graphics drivers are up to date, upgrade "
"your machine's hardware (the RAM or graphics card), and disable some options that are more memory intensive:"
msgstr ""
"要防止问题再次发生，您可以检查显卡驱动程序是最新版本，你已经升级了你的计算机硬件 （RAM 或图形卡），并禁用需要"
"内存密集型的某些选项："

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:18
msgid "Reduce undo steps :menuselection:`User Preferences --> Editing --> Undo Steps`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:20
msgid ""
"Disable *Region Overlap* and *Triple buffering* at :menuselection:`User Preferences --> System --> Window "
"Draw Method`."
msgstr "关闭 *区域重叠* 和 *三次缓冲* 在 :menuselection:`用户偏好设置 --> 系统 --> 窗口绘制方法` 。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:22
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using multisample, anti-aliasing also increases the memory usage and make display slower."
msgstr "使用多重采样，抗锯齿都会增加内存的使用量也使显示变慢。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:23
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"On Linux, the Window Manager (KDE, Gnome, Unity) may be using hardware accelerated effects (e.g. window "
"shadows and transparency) that are using up the memory that Blender needs. Try disabling the desktop effects "
"or switch to a lightweight Window Manager."
msgstr ""
"在Linux上，窗口管理器（KDE，Gnome，Unity）也许会使用硬件加速效果（比如，窗口阴影和透明）这些也会占用掉很多原"
"本Blender需要的内存。试着关闭这些桌面特效或者切换成轻量级的窗口管理器。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:29
msgid "Crash Log"
msgstr "崩溃日志"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:31
msgid ""
"When Blender crashes, it writes out a text file which contains informations that may help identify the cause "
"of the crash."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:34
msgid ""
"On a crash, a file is written based on the name of the currently loaded blend file, so ``test.blend`` will "
"create a file called ``test.crash.txt``. The crash log for unsaved files will be written into the :ref:`temp-"
"dir` directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:38
msgid "This file contains a log of tools used up until the crash as well as some other debug information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/crash.rst:40
msgid ""
"When reporting bugs on crashes it can be helpful to attach this file to your reports, especially when others "
"are unable to reproduce the crash."
msgstr ""
